data.name: INSULINE SYRINGES
data.description:
COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)
- Gasket: Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber and Natural Rubber

STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

PRESENTATIONS
- Latex and latex-free Gasket
- Customizable graduation including logo

PERFORMANCE
- Low Dead Space
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency Barrel
- Automatic Lubrication’s Technology => Optimal result on penetration resistance
- Thin wall technology => pressure reduction
- Smooth sliding
- Smooth Surface
